  "detailed_description": "This is a light puzzle game set in a vampire manor, inspired by the experience of playing the \"Castlevania series\" and combined with an understanding and reflection on vampire culture.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You wake up suddenly with an excruciating headache, in this strange room, yet there's an inexplicable sense of familiarity.<br></li><li>You try to find a way out of the castle, only to discover you're always in the same place.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/cc20f6dd9d788b908962e01c6f017f4c.poster.avif?t=1720764100\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/cc20f6dd9d788b908962e01c6f017f4c.webm?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/cc20f6dd9d788b908962e01c6f017f4c.mp4?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Through one cycle after another, you realize the manor seems to be inhabited by vampires.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/e02a212c1a9660da038ef1cbf407bcc8.poster.avif?t=1720764100\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/e02a212c1a9660da038ef1cbf407bcc8.webm?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/e02a212c1a9660da038ef1cbf407bcc8.mp4?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Failure to escape within the time limit would be a disaster.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/b4ef7aac8417dccf58fa244635741f93.poster.avif?t=1720764100\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/b4ef7aac8417dccf58fa244635741f93.webm?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/b4ef7aac8417dccf58fa244635741f93.mp4?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls：</h2>WASD - Move<br>Right click - Zoom in<br>Shift-Run<br>F-collect<br>G- Book<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2>Scrutinize everything in the scene to see if there's anything unusual.<br>If there is an anomaly, turn back immediately,<br>If there's none, keep moving forward.<br>Each exploration is time-limited.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game duration:</h2>There are three levels.<br>The duration is approximately 60-120 minutes.",
