ine poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/b4ef7aac8417dccf58fa244635741f93.poster.avif?t=1720764100\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/b4ef7aac8417dccf58fa244635741f93.webm?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016090/extras/b4ef7aac8417dccf58fa244635741f93.mp4?t=1720764100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls：</h2>WASD - Move<br>Right click - Zoom in<br>Shift-Run<br>F-collect<br>G- Book<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2>Scrutinize everything in the scene to see if there's anything unusual.<br>If there is an anomaly, turn back immediately,<br>If there's none, keep moving forward.<br>Each exploration is time-limited.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game duration:</h2>There are three levels.<br>The duration is approximately 60-120 minutes.",
